document_data.mainbody:
High Priest Gondsman Chansibral Thjestnal was ranking priest of the  High House of the Wonderful Wheel, a temple dedicated to Gond, in Ordulin in 1358 DR.
Chansibral was the leader of Gonds faithful in Ordulin. His congregation within the temple consisted of 22 other priests and 38 followers.
